title: [Olbin Pass]
description: The pass angles down to the north, its broad width stretching towards a rocky prominence set against the sky.  Smoke, or perhaps mist, rises up beyond the jagged rocks.  Shimmering, the snow underfoot twinkles dimly with reflective light, as if it were imbedded with thousands of tiny gemstones.
